Recommended Global Options

Last compiled: January 15, 2018

  • Click Tools > Global Options > R General (See Figure 1)

Figure 1: Global Options for R

  • Change the default Save workspace to .RData on exit: from Ask to Never using the drop down menu.

  • Click on Sweave in Figure 1 and change the Weave Rnw files using: from the default Sweave to knitr. (See Figure 2)

Figure 2: Global Options for Sweave
